1538.description: A magical scroll that relocates you to the nearest village Blessed Scroll of Escape

1539.name: Greater Healing Potion
1539.description: A magical potion that quickly restores HP. Its effect lasts for 15 seconds. Greater Healing Potion

1540.name: Quick Healing Potion
1540.description: A magical potion that quickly restores HP. Quick Healing Potion

1541.name: Honey Khandar
1541.description: A miraculous medicine made of the mixture of honey and khandar extract. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1542.name: Bear Fur Cloak
1542.description: A cloak made of grizzly bear's fur. Excellent for keeping warm. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1543.name: Bloody Axe
1543.description: An axe that holds the blood of wild animals. It is said to strengthen its owner's life force. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1544.name: Ancestor Skull
1544.description: A skull of an ancestor of Urutus. It is said to strengthen its owner's life force. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1545.name: Spider Dust
1545.description: A grain of powder made of dried legs of poisonous spiders. Smelling it will make you feel refreshed. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1546.name: Deep Sea Orb
1546.description: A pearl brought out of a deep sea. It is said to help predict the future. Take this to Centurion Nakusin.

1547.name: Bolter's List
1547.description: The list of things that Bolter wants you to bring from the village.

1548.name: Mining Boots
1548.description: A pair of mining boots you got from Trader Garita. Take this to Miner Bolter.

1549.name: Miner's Pick
1549.description: A miner's pick you got from Blacksmith Brunon. Take this to Miner Bolter.

1550.name: Boomboom Powder
1550.description: A sack of boomboom powder you got from Trader Shari. Take this to Miner Bolter.

1551.name: Redstone Beer
1551.description: Delicious beer you got from Warehouse Chief Reed. Take this to Miner Bolter.

1552.name: Bolter's Smelly Socks
1552.description: A pair of socks that Miner Bolter gave you. For what...?

1553.name: Hatos's 1st Order
1553.description: The order to kill Baranka's messenger. After killing him, recover the letter and take it to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1554.name: Hatos's 2nd Order
1554.description: The order states that you must kill Baranka's messenger. After killing him, recover the letter and take it to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1555.name: Hatos's 3rd Order
1555.description: The order states that you must kill Baranka's messenger. After killing him, recover the letter and take it to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1556.name: Letter to Dark Elf
1556.description: The secret letter that Baranka is sending to Dark Elven Magister Kaland. Take the letter to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1557.name: Letter to Human
1557.description: The secret letter that Baranka is sending to Duke Van Halter. Take the letter to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1558.name: Letter to Elf
1558.description: The secret letter that Baranka is sending to Elven Master Laria. Take the letter to Urutu Chief Hatos.

1559.name: Gouph's Contract
1559.description: Collector Gouph drew up this contract when buying the star diamond from Trader Reep. Take this to Trader Reep.

1560.name: Reep's Contract
1560.description: Trader Reep drew up this contract when he requested the delivery of the star diamond. Take this to Carrier Torocco.

1561.name: Elven Wine
1561.description: Carrier Torocco bought this high quality wine to give it to his old friend, Maron, as a present. Take this to Miner Maron.

1562.name: Brunon's Dice
1562.description: These dice were specially made for gambling. Take these to Blacksmith Brunon.

1563.name: Brunon's Contract
1563.description: This contract says if Brunon gets the 20 stolen jewels back from goblins, he can get the star diamond back.

1564.name: Aquamarine
1564.description: This jewel is obtained by the goblin brigand leader. Take 10 aquamarines and 10 chrysoberyls to Blacksmith Brunon.

1565.name: Chrysoberyl
1565.description: This jewel is obtained by the goblin brigand leader. Take 10 aquamarines and 10 chrysoberyls to Blacksmith Brunon.

1566.name: Gem Box
1566.description: Blacksmith Brunon gives this gem box. Take it to Collector Gouph.

1567.name: Coal Piece
1567.description: This coal piece is in the gem box. Take this to Blacksmith Brunon.

1568.name: Brunon's Letter
1568.description: Blacksmith Brunon sends this letter to Warehouse Keeper Murdoc asking for the right box.

1569.name: Berry Tart
1569.description: Sweet strawberry-flavored tart. Warehouse Keeper Murdoc sends this to Warehouse Keeper Airy as a present of apology.

1570.name: Bat Diagram
1570.description: This diagram shows the blade bat in details. Take this and go hunt blade bats to obtain the star diamond.

1571.name: Star Diamond
1571.description: Everyone is looking for this diamond. Take this to the real owner.

1572.name: Starstone
1572.description: A mineral collected from the destroyed greystone golem. Collect 20 of these and take them to Gatekeeper Tamil.

1573.name: Starstone
1573.description: A mineral obtained by defeated whinstone golems. Collect twenty and take them to Gatekeeper Wirphy.

1574.name: Mirien's Review
1574.description: A letter Magister Mirien wrote after tasting Jonas's dish. Take this and go to Jonas.

1575.name: Mirien's Review
1575.description: A letter Magister Mirien wrote after tasting Jonas's dish. Take this to Jonas.

1576.description: A letter Magister Mirien wrote after tasting Jonas's dish. Take this to Jonas.

1577.description: A letter Magister Mirien wrote after tasting Jonas's dish. Take this to Jonas.

1578.name: Green Blood
1578.description: Goblin's blood. If you have enough of this item, the Kuruka ratman leader appears.

1579.name: Goblin Dwelling Map
1579.description: A map showing goblins' dwelling. Take this and find the goblin tribes and destroy them.

1580.name: Kuruka Ratman Tooth
1580.description: A tooth obtained after killing Kuruka ratman leader. Collect ten of these to take to Prefect Karukia.

1581.name: Betrayer's Report
1581.description: A detailed account of a betrayer who recently joined the Umbar tribe and settled on the outskirts of a mountain west of the Spider Nest.

1591.name: Head of Betrayer
1591.description: The head of a traitor orc. Collect 2 and take them to Prefect Kasman in Gludin Village.

1592.name: Mark of Raider
1592.description: A necklace given to an Orc who has earned the qualification to become an Orc Raider. Take this to the high prefect to change your occupation to an Orc Raider.

1593.name: Pomegranate
1593.description: A red pomegranate fruit given by Gantaki. Take this and go to Khavatari Rosheek.

1594.name: 1st Leather Pouch
1594.description: A leather pouch given by Khavatari Rosheek. Take this and hunt kasha bears and collect 5 of their claws.

1595.name: 2nd Leather Pouch
1595.description: A leather pouch given by Khavatari Rosheek. Hunt kasha blade spiders with this and collect 5 talons.

1596.name: 3rd Leather Pouch
1596.description: A leather pouch Khavatari Rosheek gave you. Take this while hunting scarlet salamanders to obtain 5 of their scales.

1597.name: 1st Leather Pouch (Full)
1597.description: A pouch that contains 5 kasha bear claws. Take this to Khavatari Rosheek.

1598.name: 2nd Leather Pouch (Full)
1598.description: A pouch that contains 5 pincers of kasha blade spider talon. Take this to Khavatari Rosheek.

1599.name: 3rd Leather Pouch (Full)
1599.description: A pouch that contains 5 scales from the scarlet salamander. Take this to Khavatari Rosheek.
